title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Putting the IP in RIP Pt. II with Trey Kerby
description:
We’re going back-to-back, folks. Trey and the boys are clicking like the new big 3 behind the paywall, dropping dimes, yamming on fools and getting absolutely wetty from downtown. It’s game time and we’re digging deep on doing the most, how to succeed as a full-time podcaster, handling fame, losing your intellectual property, basketball media, Barstool sports, The Last Dance, Jordan’s voice, Pippen’s hog, fatherhood, the NBA sidepiece economy and much more on this Patreon-exclusive episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
